**LD:**             

RUST logical disk driver LD:

LD: treats (container) disk files as disk volumes.
[[code format="text"]]
  SET LD: EMPTY           ! Dismount all units  
  SET LD: CLEAN           ! Remount all mounted units
[[code]]
* Container files must have the filetype ".DSK".
* RUST sub-directories are an alternative to logical disks.
* For more information see [[Mount_Command|MOUNT]]


